\c 18
\s Jeturo anoshanyira Mozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jeturo\x + 2.18. 3.1.\x*, mupristi weMidhiani\x + 18.12. 2.16.\x*, mukarahwa waMozisi, wakati anzwa zvose Jehovha zvaakaitira Mozisi naIsraeri vanhu vake, kuti Jehovha wakabudisa Israeri kubva muEgipita,
\v 2 Jeturo mukarahwa waMozisi ndokutora Zipora mukadzi waMozisi shure kwekunge amudzosera\x + 4.26.\x*,
\v 3 nevanakomana vake vaviri\x + Mab. 7.29.\x*, avo zita reumwe raiva Gerishomu, nokuti wakati: Ndaiva mweni panyika yeutorwa;
\v 4 nezita reumwe raiva Eriazari, nokuti \add wakati\add*: Mwari wababa vangu waiva ari mubatsiri wangu, uye wakandinunura pamunondo waFarao\x + Gen.. 4.25; 26.7; 32.30; 41.51,52. 2 Sam. 9.11; 18.23. Job. 32.17. Jer. 4.31; 6.17; 20.10. Mako 6.9. Mab. 1.4.\x*.
\v 5 Jeturo mukarahwa waMozisi ndokuuya kuna Mozisi ane vanakomana vake nemukadzi wake murenje, paaiva akavaka musasa, pagomo raMwari\x + 3.1,12.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino wakati kuna Mozisi: Ini mukarahwa wako Jeturo ndauya kwauri, nemukadzi wako nevanakomana vake vaviri vanaye.
\v 7 Mozisi ndokubuda kunochingamidza mukarahwa wake\x + Gen.. 14.17; 18.2; 19.1. 1 Madz. 2.19.\x*, ndokukotama, ndokumutsvoda\x + Gen.. 29.13; 33.4. 2 Sam. 19.39.\x*. Zvino vakabvunzana upenyu, ndokupinda mutende.
\v 8 Zvino Mozisi wakaudza mukarahwa wake zvose Jehovha zvaakaitira Farao neVaEgipita nekuda kwaIsraeri, dambudziko rose rakavawira panzira, Jehovha ndokuvanunura.
\v 9 Jeturo ndokufara pamusoro pezvakanaka zvose Jehovha zvaaiva aitira Israeri\x + Job. 3.6.\x* waaiva anunura kubva paruoko rweVaEgipita.
\v 10 Jeturo ndokuti: Jehovha ngaarumbidzwe\x + Gen.. 14.20. 2 Sam. 18.28. Ruk. 1.68.\x* iye wakakununurai kubva paruoko rweVaEgipita, nekubva paruoko rwaFarao, iye wakanunura vanhu kubva pasi peruoko rweVaEgipita.
\v 11 Ikozvino ndaziva kuti Jehovha mukuru kupfuura vamwari vose, nokuti pachinhu\x + 1.10,16,22; 5.2,7; 14.18.\x* chavakazvitutumadza nacho waiva pamusoro pavo\x + Neh. 9.10,16,29. Map. 119.21. Ruk. 1.51.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino Jeturo, mukarahwa waMozisi, wakatora chipo chinopiswa nezvibairo kuna Mwari; Aroni ndokupinda pamwe nevakuru vose vaIsraeri kuzodya chingwa nemukarahwa waMozisi pamberi paMwari\x + Det. 12.7. 14.26. 1 Makor. 29.21,22. Gen.. 31.54. 24.11.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Zvino zvakaitika chifume, kuti Mozisi wakagara kutonga vanhu; vanhu ndokumira naMozisi kubva mangwanani kusvika madekwani.
\v 14 Mukarahwa waMozisi wakati achiona zvose zvaaiitira vanhu, wakati: Chii ichi chaunoitira vanhu? Unogarirei wega, vanhu vose vachimira newe kubva mangwanani kusvika madekwani?
\v 15 Mozisi ndokuti kumukarahwa wake: Nokuti vanhu vanouya kwandiri kuzobvunza kuna Mwari\x + Rev. 24.12. Num.. 15.34.\x*.
\v 16 Kana vane nyaya\x + 23.7. 24.14. Det. 17.8. 2 Sam. 15.2,3. 1 VaKori. 6.1.\x* vanouya kwandiri; uye ndinotonga pakati peuyu neumwe, uye ndinozivisa mitemo yaMwari nemirairo yake\x + Rev. 24.15. Num.. 15.35; 27.6; 36.6.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino mukarahwa waMozisi wakati kwaari: Chinhu chaunoita hachina kunaka.
\v 18 Zvirokwazvo uchaneta, zvose iwe nevanhu ava vaunavo; nokuti chinhu ichi chinorema kwazvo kwauri; haungagoni kuchiita pachako woga\x + Num.. 11.14,17. Det. 1.9,12.\x*.
\v 19 Teerera ikozvino kuinzwi rangu, ndichakupa zano, uye Mwari achava newe\x + 3.12.\x*. Iwe iva wevanhu kuna Mwari\x + 4.16. 20.19. Det. 5.5.\x*, uye iwe uise nyaya \add dzavo\add* kuna Mwari\x + Num.. 27.5.\x*;
\v 20 uye uchavadzidzisa mitemo nemirairo\x + Map. 19.11. Eze. 33.3,.\x*, ugovazivisa nzira yavanofamba nayo\x + Map. 143.8.\x*, nebasa ravanoita\x + Det. 1.18.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino iwe uone kubva pakati pevanhu vose varume vane simba\x + 18.25. Det. 1.15,16; 16.18. 2 Makor. 19.5-10. Mab. 6.3.\x*, vanotya Mwari\x + Gen.. 42.18. 2 Sam. 23.3. 2 Makor. 19.9.\x*, varume vechokwadi\x + Eze. 18.8.\x*, vanovenga mubairo usakarurama\x + Det. 16.19.\x*; uvaise pamusoro pavo, \add vave\add* vatungamiriri vezvuru, vatungamiriri vemazana, vatungamiriri vemakumi mashanu, nevatungamiriri vemakumi;
\v 22 kuti vatonge vanhu nguva dzese\x + 18.26.\x*; zvino zvichaitika \add kuti\add* nyaya huru imwe neimwe vachaiuisa kwauri, asi nyaya imwe neimwe diki ivo ngavaitonge\x + 18.26. Rev. 24.11. Num.. 15.33. 27.2. 36.1. Det. 1.17; 17.8.\x*; zvino iwe uchazvirerusira, uye vachatakudzana newe\x + Num.. 11.17.\x*.
\v 23 Kana uchiita chinhu ichi, Mwari achakurairawo, zvino iwe uchagona kumira\x + 18.18.\x*, nevanhu ava vose vachaendawo kunzvimbo yavo nerugare\x + Gen.. 18.33; 30.25; 31.55. 2 Sam. 19.39.\x*.
\v 24 Mozisi ndokuteerera kuinzwi remukarahwa wake, ndokuita zvose zvaaiva ataura.
\v 25 Mozisi ndokusarudza varume vane simba kubva kuna Israeri wose\x + Det. 1.15.\x*, ndokuvaita vatungamiriri pamusoro pevanhu, vatungamiriri vezvuru, vatungamiriri vemazana, vatungamiriri vemakumi mashanu, nevatungamiriri vemakumi.
\v 26 Zvino vakatonga vanhu nguva dzese\x + Gen.. 18.33; 30.25; 31.55; 16.29. 2 Sam. 19.39.\x*; nyaya dzakaoma ndokudziuisa kuna Mozisi, asi nyaya imwe neimwe diki vaitonga vomene.
\p
\v 27 Zvino Mozisi wakarega mukarahwa akaenda; zvino akaenda kunyika yekwake\x + Num.. 10.29,30.\x*.